climate

Class ClimateRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • climate.ClimateRecord

  • public class ClimateRecord
extends java.lang.Object
    This class holds a record of climate data. Each record is a line from the file, separated by the comma delimiter. Holding each record within its own object allows for easy sorting.
    Author:
    Marcus Lorenzana
